  .mdc-text-field {
    border-radius: var(--mdc-shape-small, 4px);
    padding-inline: var(--textfield-padding-inline, 12px);
  }

  label.mdc-text-field--filled {
    height: var(--textfield-height, 30px);
  }

  .mdc-text-field .mdc-text-field__input {
    caret-color: var(--cros-textfield-cursor-color-focus);
    font-weight: var(--textfield-font-weight, normal);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: var(--ea-textfield-text-align, initial);
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  :host([dir='rtl']) .mdc-text-field .mdc-text-field__input {
    direction: rtl;
  }

  .mdc-text-field {
    background-color: var(--mdc-text-field-fill-color);
  }

  .mdc-text-field--outlined {
    height: 32px;
  }

  :host([type='password']) .mdc-text-field .mdc-text-field__input {
    font-size: calc(var(--textfield-height) / 2);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  }

  .mdc-text-field .mdc-text-field__input::selection {
    background: var(--cros-text-highlight-color);

  .mdc-text-field + .mdc-text-field-helper-line {

  .mdc-text-field-character-counter {
    margin-inline-end: 0;
    padding-inline-end: 0;

  .mdc-text-field--disabled .mdc-text-field__affix--suffix,
  .mdc-text-field:not(.mdc-text-field--disabled)

    color: var(--cros-textfield-suffixes-color);
  }

  .mdc-text-field.mdc-text-field--invalid:not(.mdc-text-field--disabled)

    border-bottom-color: transparent;
    caret-color: var(--cros-textfield-cursor-color-error);

    color: var(--cros-textfield-hint-text-color-error);
  }

  .mdc-text-field__affix--suffix {
    padding-inline: 12px 0;
